Description: The guitar pictured is the actual guitar you will receive!Zakk adds his signature "twist" to the classic Les Paul Custom with a Mah body and a Hard Maple neck, which has an ultra-smooth and fast natural satin finish that allows you to solo effortlessly. The Zakk Wylde Bullseye Les Paul Custom features a pair of sizzling EMG Active humbucker pickups, Tune-o-Matic bridge, Grover machine heads, a bound body and headstock, gold hardware and Zakk's signature graphics.This guitar also has Zakk's signature on it - the signature has been verified by Will Jones of Epiphone as being Zakk's authentic signature. Comes with the original Epiphone hardshell case and warranty info card. According to the serial number, this guitar was made in 2005, made in Korea.This Zakk Wylde Epi is bad ass! EMGs installed and also new 9V installed. Zakk Wylde himself signed it.....took photo with me of it. He even played it (not plugged in) and thought it was set up perfect. I had the rest of Black Lavel Society signed it. This was 2014 in Southern NJ. A night I will never forget. It is your turn to own this iconic axe!!!! It plays like a dream....and will SCREAM!!!Please give her a new home?Free shipping if purchased at my price.
Title: Epiphone Les Paul Zakk Wylde Bullseye Electric Guitar/signed by Zakk and BLS
